title: Euro Likely to Challenge Important Resistance Levels
text:
Fri, Jul 24, 2015, 1:47 AM AEST - Australia Markets open in 8 hrs 13 mins Euro Likely to Challenge Important Resistance Levels By David Rodriguez | DailyFX – 1 hour 32 minutes ago Recommend Rec eive the Weekly Speculative Sentiment Index report via PDF via David’s e-mail distribution list . EURUSD – The Euro has bounced notably off of recent lows and rallies have been met with retail FX trader selling. A contrarian view of herd sentiment gives us reason to watch for continued gains. The pair will see an important test at major volume-based congestion resistance at $1.10 , but a close above would leave little in the way of major resistance until $1.1250.
